    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "Vanish In A Splash",
        "Description": "In Japanese myth, there is a story of a \u2018Magic Koi\u2019 which possesses mystical powers. Some say if the legendary creature splashes even a drop on a person, they will vanish into thin air, as if they never existed.\rA mysterious local informed us of a supposed sighting of this fantastical fish in Hokkaido; investigate the veracity of his claim, and should it hold water, test the extent of its abilities by making some bodies disappear.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as Codename-24.",
